376
00:25:52,827 --> 00:25:54,276
Apa maksudmu?

377
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:57,210
Oh, kau tahu, semangat zaman.

378
00:25:57,314 --> 00:26:00,006
Astaga.

379
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:03,769
