416
00:29:21,414 --> 00:29:25,177
Sial! Tunggu,
aku menelepon bantuan, oke?

417
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:26,316
Aah!

418
00:29:30,976 --> 00:29:32,943
Kenapa ini punya
begitu banyak tayangan?

419
00:29:33,047 --> 00:29:36,084
- Apa yang kau tonton?
